#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "How do we measure startup time"
msgstr "我们如何衡量启动时间"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Some frameworks use aggressive lazy initialization techniques.\n"
"It is important to measure the time to first request (TTFR) to most accurately reflect how long a framework needs to start.\n"
"Otherwise, you will miss the time the framework _actually_ takes to initialize."
msgstr "有些框架采用了激进的延迟初始化技术。测量首次请求时间（TTFR）非常重要，这样才能最准确地反映框架启动所需的时间。否则，你会忽略框架 _实际_ 初始化所花费的时间。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Here is how we measure startup time in our tests."
msgstr "以下是我们在测试中衡量启动时间的方法。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Approach"
msgstr "方法"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We record a timestamp immediately before launching the application, start polling the application's HTTP endpoint, launch, and then continue polling until it returns a 200 response. The difference is the Time to First Request (TTFR)."
msgstr "我们在启动应用程序之前立即记录一个时间戳，开始轮询该应用程序的 HTTP 端点，启动应用程序，然后继续轮询，直到其返回 200 状态码。其中的差异即为“首次请求时间”（TTFR）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison/blob/main/scripts/perf-lab/scripts/time-to-1st-request.sh[`time-to-1st-request.sh`] script in the benchmark repository implements this precisely. It records the start time using nanosecond granularity:"
msgstr "基准测试代码库中的 ` link:https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison/blob/main/scripts/perf-lab/scripts/time-to-1st-request.sh[time-to-1st-request.sh] ` 脚本正是为此而实现的。它以纳秒为单位记录开始时间："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "On macOS, the built-in `date` does not support `%N`. Install GNU coreutils and use `gdate +%s%N` instead."
msgstr "在 macOS 上，内置的 `日期` 格式不支持 `%N` 。请安装 GNU coreutils，并改用 `gdate +%s%N` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A background polling loop attempts TCP connections and sends HTTP GET requests until a 200 response is received:"
msgstr "一个后台轮询循环会不断尝试建立 TCP 连接并发送 HTTP GET 请求，直到收到 200 状态码的响应为止："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The TTFR is then computed as the difference between the response timestamp and the start timestamp, in nanoseconds."
msgstr "随后，TTFR 通过响应时间戳与起始时间戳之间的差值（以纳秒为单位）计算得出。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Why not just use the framework's reported startup time?"
msgstr "为什么不直接使用框架报告的启动时间呢？"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A framework-reported startup time (e.g. \"started in 0.002s\") only measures internal initialization.\n"
"It will not include time spent loading shared libraries, JVM bootstrap, and there may also be a further gap between the claimed ready-time and the time when the application can actually serve a request.\n"
"Measuring TTFR end-to-end captures the full cost."
msgstr "框架报告的启动时间（例如“0.002 秒内启动”）仅衡量内部初始化过程。该时间不包含加载共享库和 JVM 引导所耗费的时间，且宣称的就绪时间与应用程序实际能够处理请求的时间之间可能还存在进一步的延迟。 而测量端到端的 TTFR 则能全面反映总耗时。"

