#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "JVM flags for benchmarking"
msgstr "用于基准测试的 JVM 参数"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The benchmark scripts apply these JVM flags when running the application under test:"
msgstr "基准测试脚本在运行被测应用程序时会应用以下 JVM 参数："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`-XX:ActiveProcessorCount` limits how many processors the JVM believes are available, ensuring consistent thread pool sizing across environments.\n"
"`-Xms` and `-Xmx` are set to the same value to eliminate heap resizing during the measurement."
msgstr "`-XX:ActiveProcessorCount` 用于限制 JVM 认为可用的处理器数量，以确保不同环境下的线程池大小保持一致。将 `-Xms` 和 `-Xmx` 设置为相同值，以避免在测量过程中发生堆大小调整。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In the performance lab, CPU affinity is further controlled using `taskset` to pin processes to specific cores, preventing interference between the application, database, load generator, and monitoring."
msgstr "在性能实验室中，通过使用 `taskset` 进一步控制 CPU 亲和性，将进程绑定到特定核心，从而防止应用程序、数据库、负载生成器和监控工具之间相互干扰。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Additional flags applied by Quarkus"
msgstr "Quarkus应用的其他标志"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When Quarkus invokes GraalVM `native-image` it will apply some additional flags by default."
msgstr "当Quarkus调用GraalVM `native-image` ，它将默认应用一些额外的标志。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You might want to know about the following ones in case you're comparing performance properties with other builds."
msgstr "你可能想知道以下这些，以防你与其他建筑的性能属性进行比较。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Disable fallback images"
msgstr "禁用后备图像"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Fallback native images are a feature of GraalVM to \"fall back\" to run your application in the normal JVM, should the compilation\n"
"to native code fail for some reason."
msgstr "回退本地镜像是 GraalVM 的一项功能，当编译为本地代码的过程因某种原因失败时，它可以 \"回退 \"到正常的 JVM 中运行应用程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus disables this feature by setting `-H:FallbackThreshold=0`: this will ensure you get a compilation failure rather\n"
"risking to not notice that the application is unable to really run in native mode."
msgstr "Quarkus 通过设置 `-H:FallbackThreshold=0` 来禁用这一功能：这将确保编译失败，而不是冒着应用程序无法真正在本地模式下运行的风险。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you instead want to just run in Java mode, that's totally possible: just skip the native-image build and run it as a jar."
msgstr "如果你只想在Java模式下运行，那是完全可能的：只要跳过本地图像构建，以jar的形式运行。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Disable Isolates"
msgstr "禁用隔离器"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Isolates are a neat feature of GraalVM, but Quarkus isn't using them at this stage."
msgstr "隔离器是GraalVM的一个很好的功能，但是Quarkus在这个阶段并没有使用它们。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Disable via `-H:-SpawnIsolates`."
msgstr "通过 `-H:-SpawnIsolates` 停用。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Disable auto-registration of all Service Loader implementations"
msgstr "禁用所有服务加载器实现的自动注册功能"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus extensions can automatically pick the right services they need, while GraalVM's native-image defaults to include\n"
"all services it's able to find on the classpath."
msgstr "Quarkus 扩展可以自动选择所需的服务，而 GraalVM 的本地镜像则默认包含它能在类路径上找到的所有服务。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We prefer listing services explicitly as it produces better optimised binaries. Disable it as well by setting `-H:-UseServiceLoaderFeature`."
msgstr "我们更喜欢明确列出服务，因为它能产生更好的优化的二进制文件。通过设置 `-H:-UseServiceLoaderFeature` ，也可以禁用它。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Others ..."
msgstr "其他..."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This section is provided as high level guidance, but can't presume to be comprehensive as some flags are controlled\n"
" dynamically by the extensions, the platform you're building on, configuration details, your code and possibly\n"
" a combination of these."
msgstr "本节提供的是高水平的指导，但并不全面，因为有些标志是由扩展、构建平台、配置细节、代码动态控制的，也可能是这些因素的组合。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Generally speaking the ones listed here are those most likely to affect performance metrics, but in the right\n"
"circumstances one could observe non-negligible impact from the other flags too."
msgstr "一般来说，这里列出的是最有可能影响性能指标的标志，但在适当的情况下，也可以观察到其他标志带来的不可忽视的影响。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you're to investigate some differences in detail make sure to check what Quarkus is invoking exactly: when the build\n"
"plugin is producing a native image, the full command lines are logged."
msgstr "如果你想详细调查一些差异，请务必检查 Quarkus 调用的具体内容：当构建插件生成本地镜像时，会记录完整的命令行。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Coordinated Omission Problem in Tools"
msgstr "工具中的协调遗漏问题"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When measuring performance of a framework like Quarkus the latency experience by users are especially interesting and for that there are many different tools. Unfortunately, many fail to measure the latency correctly and instead fall short and create the Coordinate Omission problem. Meaning tools fails to accommodate for delays to submit new requests when system is under load and aggregate these numbers making the latency and throughput numbers very misleading."
msgstr "在衡量 Quarkus 这类框架的性能时，用户实际感受到的延迟尤为值得关注，为此也有许多不同的工具。 遗憾的是，许多工具无法正确测量延迟，反而存在不足，从而导致“坐标遗漏”问题。这意味着这些工具未能考虑到系统负载较高时提交新请求的延迟，却将这些数据汇总计算，导致延迟和吞吐量数据极具误导性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A good walkthrough of the issue is https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lJ8ydIuPFeU[this video] where Gil Tene the author of wrk2 explains the issue and https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xdG8b9iDYbE[Quarkus Insights #22] have John O'Hara from Quarkus performance team show how it can show up."
msgstr "关于这个问题，wrk2 的作者 Gil Tene 在 link:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lJ8ydIuPFeU[这段视频] 中做了很好的解释， link:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xdG8b9iDYbE[Quarkus Insights #22] 中 Quarkus 性能团队的 John O'Hara 也展示了这个问题是如何出现的。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Although that video and related papers and articles date all back to 2015 then even today you will find tools that fall short with the coordinated omission problem."
msgstr "尽管那段视频及相关论文和文章都可追溯至2015年，但即便是今天，你仍然会发现有些工具在处理“协调性遗漏”问题时仍显不足。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Tools that at current time of writing are known to exhibit the problem and should NOT be used for measuring latency/throughput (they may be used for other things):"
msgstr "截至本文撰写之时，已知存在该问题的工具，不应用于测量延迟/吞吐量（但可用于其他用途）："

